more times than you can count?

08:42.355 --> 08:44.657
Under these circumstances,

08:44.658 --> 08:46.659
no, I've never done this before.

08:46.660 --> 08:48.027
Let's leave all the lawyer

08:48.028 --> 08:50.197
out here on the porch,
know what I mean?

09:17.224 --> 09:18.558
<i>[speaking Spanish]</i>

09:19.893 --> 09:21.094
No.

09:22.730 --> 09:24.097
<i>[speaking Spanish]</i>

09:25.098 --> 09:26.565
I mean, kind of.

09:26.566 --> 09:28.636
<i>[speaking Spanish]</i>

09:31.471 --> 09:32.605
What this means,

09:32.606 --> 09:34.540
this section here,

09:34.541 --> 09:38.244
is that accepting these funds
does not nullify

09:38.245 --> 09:40.780
any insurance policy
your husbands may have had,

09:40.781 --> 09:42.882
and they each had term policies
through the company

09:42.883 --> 09:45.417
with death benefits of $25,000.

09:45.418 --> 09:47.655
What are we
supposed to do with $25,000?

09:48.689 --> 09:51.724
It is a nominal amount
to cover funeral expenses.

09:51.725 --> 09:54.761
It's standard through
your medical insurance.

09:54.762 --> 09:56.697
<i>[speaking Spanish]</i>

09:57.698 --> 09:59.098
What about
our medical insurance?

09:59.099 --> 10:00.933
Your policy will COBRA,

10:00.934 --> 10:03.803
which means that you will remain
on the policy for 18 months.

10:03.804 --> 10:07.975
Then, you can extend the policy
at your own expense.

10:13.914 --> 10:17.550
