Call me if you need anything.

33:26.038 --> 33:27.172
I'll be back tomorrow.

33:27.173 --> 33:28.707
Thank you.

33:34.180 --> 33:35.713
[sighs]

33:35.714 --> 33:38.183
Nothing's going on.

33:38.184 --> 33:40.952
Her husband just died.

33:42.254 --> 33:44.155
I'm trying...

33:44.156 --> 33:46.857
She called and asked for help,
and I gave it.

33:46.858 --> 33:49.860
She's not my concern. You are.

33:49.861 --> 33:51.729
And at the moment,

33:51.730 --> 33:54.999
the fuckers that put you in this
hospital are my main concern.

33:55.000 --> 33:56.434
If my father steps in...

33:56.435 --> 33:58.169
This is not your dad talking.

33:58.170 --> 34:00.705
This is the general manager
of an oil company talking.

34:00.706 --> 34:03.408
And when my employees
break into another employee's

34:03.409 --> 34:05.243
company-provided housing

34:05.244 --> 34:07.312
and beat the dog shit out of him
to the point where a surgeon

34:07.313 --> 34:09.781
has to re-inflate his lung,
I step in.

34:12.584 --> 34:15.220
Manuel and Antonio.

34:15.221 --> 34:16.788
Who else?

34:19.758 --> 34:23.329
You can tell me, or I'll beat it
out of the first two.

34:26.332 --> 34:28.234
I don't know their names.

34:29.768 --> 34:31.970
Maintenance crew
for the buffalo field.

34:33.739 --> 34:35.207
That's all you had to say.

34:37.509 --> 34:39.278
You're gonna have to move slow
with this girl.

34:41.113 --> 34:43.248
She's hurting in a way
that you can't understand,

34:43.249 --> 34:45.250
and she's trying to find
somewhere to put it.

34:45.251 --> 34:47.385
It's not like that.

34:47.386 --> 34:49.154
How many other widows
do you think

34:49.155 --> 34:51.257
are sitting in this hospital
tonight with their helpers?

34:57.363 --> 35:00.598
This ain't the first time you
took a beating over this girl.

35:00.599 --> 35:03.301
This is the kind of beating
you get

35:03.302 --> 35:04.636
when the first one didn't take.

35:06.272 --> 35:08.674
[phone buzzing]

35:10.842 --> 35:11.842
Yeah?

35:11.843 --> 35:13.778
He just got to his trailer.

35:13.779 --> 35:15.346
[Tommy over phone]
<i>Alone?</i>

35:15.347 --> 35:16.814
- With his roommate.
<i>- All right,</i>

35:16.815 --> 35:18.483
<i>I want you
to turn those cameras off</i>

35:18.484 --> 35:20.785
and don't cut 'em back on
till I tell you, all right?

35:20.786 --> 35:22.087
Yes, sir.

35:24.323 --> 35:26.491
<i>♪ intense, dramatic music</i>

35:26.492 --> 35:28.426
Can we talk to him now?

35:28.427 --> 35:29.960
No need.

35:29.961 --> 35:32.831
Meet me at the man camp.
Give me a ten minute head start.

35:37.503 --> 35:40.172
[indistinct P.A. announcement]

35:43.141 --> 35:46.511
I'm really relaxed now.
Can I go see him?

35:46.512 --> 35:48.247
He's all yours.

35:49.047 --> 35:50.381
You got plans tonight?

35:50.382 --> 35:52.116
Soon as you give 'em to me.

35:52.117 --> 35:53.684
Let's go.

35:53.685 --> 35:55.486
Hey, don't let her drive.

35:55.487 --> 35:57.054
<i>♪ suspenseful music</i>

35:57.055 --> 35:59.191
<i>***</i>

36:01.593 --> 36:03.094
Mm.

36:07.233 --> 36:09.300
<i>♪ tense, suspenseful music</i>

36:09.301 --> 36:11.870
<i>***</i>

36:29.388 --> 36:31.423
[truck doors close]

36:38.129 --> 36:39.298
You want something?

36:41.066 --> 36:42.368
Don't leave home without it.

36:45.737 --> 36:48.274
We might not even get to use it.

36:51.243 --> 36:53.144
[crowd cheering over TV]

36:54.246 --> 36:56.381
You should just
cut that fucking thing off.

36:56.382 --> 36:58.249
Ain't your hand
that got smashed.

36:58.250 --> 37:00.518
[indistinct commentary over TV]

37:00.519 --> 37:03.053
[knocking on door]

37:03.054 --> 37:05.723
- You got a bitch coming over?
- Not till I get paid.

37:05.724 --> 37:07.493
[chuckles]

37:10.429 --> 37:12.897
Fuck. It's the boss.

37:12.898 --> 37:16.233
Don't answer.
Make like we're asleep.

37:16.234 --> 37:17.703
I can fucking hear you.

37:23.475 --> 37:26.278
What's up? [grunting]

37:33.752 --> 37:36.322
This seem familiar, motherfucker?

37:40.959 --> 37:41.993
Hey, man...

37:44.396 --> 37:45.997
[grunting]

37:51.303 --> 37:54.805
You get on your fucking phone
and call your friends.

37:54.806 --> 37:56.641
You know, the ones
that you called that put

37:56.642 --> 37:58.576
my fucking son in the hospital.

37:58.577 --> 38:00.579
[panting]

38:02.348 --> 38:03.648
No?

38:03.649 --> 38:05.416
He don't want to call
his friends, Boss.

38:05.417 --> 38:07.585
Me and my boys will
take him in the back.

38:07.586 --> 38:08.753
[Tommy]
Okay, I'd appreciate that.

38:08.754 --> 38:09.820
Oh, we'll convince you.

38:09.821 --> 38:10.955
- Come on.
- No. No, fuck.

38:10.956 --> 38:12.657
[groaning]

38:12.658 --> 38:14.359
[Boss]
Let's talk.

38:14.360 --> 38:15.526
[Antonio]
No!

38:15.527 --> 38:17.496
- [yelling]
- [blows landing]

38:21.533 --> 38:24.134
- [grunts]
- Nobody said "get up," Manny.

38:24.135 --> 38:26.505
[Antonio cries out]

38:27.839 --> 38:29.708
[groans]

38:31.677 --> 38:33.778
Have a seat, Manuel.

38:33.779 --> 38:35.414
[coughs]

38:40.686 --> 38:42.820
[Tommy]
Here's how this is gonna go.

38:42.821 --> 38:44.989
Needless to say, you're fired.

38:44.990 --> 38:47.392
By noon tomorrow,
you'll be on a "no hire" list

38:47.393 --> 38:50.160
for every fucking oil company
in the Permian Basin.

38:50.161 --> 38:52.196
Sheriff's gonna be here
in about five minutes,

38:52.197 --> 38:54.198
and he's gonna toss
this fucking place.

38:54.199 --> 38:56.066
And I'm just guessing he'll add

38:56.067 --> 38:58.369
felon in possession
of a firearm,

38:58.370 --> 39:00.705
possession of
a controlled substance,

39:00.706 --> 39:03.574
and maybe possession of
a controlled substance

39:03.575 --> 39:05.810
with intent to distribute.

39:05.811 --> 39:09.213
And any goddamn one of those
violates your parole.

39:09.214 --> 39:10.848
And then you add

39:10.849 --> 39:12.383
on top of that shit,

39:12.384 --> 39:15.052
aggravated assault charge
and kidnapping,

39:15.053 --> 39:16.987
'cause when you
shut the door on him,

39:16.988 --> 39:18.424
that's kidnapping.

39:20.459 --> 39:22.092
I ain't a goddamn mathematician,

39:22.093 --> 39:23.861
but that's, like, 30 years.

39:23.862 --> 39:25.430
- [Antonio shouts]
- [Tommy] That's what I do

39:25.431 --> 39:27.498
to people who hurt my family.

39:27.499 --> 39:29.567
You fucked
with the wrong hillbilly.

39:29.568 --> 39:31.970
[siren whooping]

39:33.672 --> 39:36.574
I'm gonna take 30 years
of your life away from you.

39:36.575 --> 39:40.044
And if you ever come back
to this place,

39:40.045 --> 39:41.546
I'm gonna take the rest of it.

39:41.547 --> 39:43.514
<i>♪ tense, dramatic music</i>

39:43.515 --> 39:45.049
<i>***</i>

39:45.050 --> 39:46.617
[indistinct radio chatter]

39:46.618 --> 39:48.218
[Antonio groaning]

39:48.219 --> 39:49.554
[Tommy]
Have you met the sheriff?

39:49.555 --> 39:52.958
[sighs] Stand up
and turn around.

39:54.460 --> 39:56.161
[grunts]

39:57.128 --> 39:59.598
They're having a confession
in the back room.

40:00.932 --> 40:02.534
Tommy.

40:03.569 --> 40:05.069
Did he have anything to say?

40:05.070 --> 40:06.737
He gave up the names.

40:06.738 --> 40:08.573
Even wrote 'em down for you.

40:08.574 --> 40:11.041
You think he'd repeat 'em to me?

40:11.042 --> 40:12.578
Sure he would if you asked.

40:20.151 --> 40:22.086
Would you confirm the names
of the other assailants?

40:22.087 --> 40:23.588
[panting]

40:23.589 --> 40:25.823
You-you gonna take me with you?

40:25.824 --> 40:27.625
[Walt]
Well, that depends.

40:27.626 --> 40:29.394
You gonna say something
give me a reason?

40:30.996 --> 40:32.262
I'll give you a reason.

40:32.263 --> 40:34.431
You boys give us a minute?

40:34.432 --> 40:36.568
[Antonio panting]

40:40.672 --> 40:42.808
[crying]

40:43.775 --> 40:45.743
<i>♪ tense, dramatic music</i>

40:45.744 --> 40:47.846
<i>***</i>

40:55.587 --> 40:57.923
[Dale] <i>Haven't done anything
like that since...</i>

40:59.625 --> 41:01.226
<i>...2016.</i>

41:04.963 --> 41:07.365
Place is getting wild again.

41:12.838 --> 41:15.774
I got to get my boy out of here
before somebody kills him.

41:17.342 --> 41:19.545
Nah, we run the killers off.

41:23.181 --> 41:25.683
There's something about that
boy, just draws trouble to him

41:25.684 --> 41:27.886
like bugs to a light.

41:31.790 --> 41:34.593
He ain't mean enough
for this place, Dale.

41:46.905 --> 41:48.673
He just ain't mean enough.

41:48.674 --> 41:50.809
<i>♪ "Sunshine"
by The Red Clay Strays ♪</i>

41:55.614 --> 42:00.719
<i>♪ There's no shame
in being broken-hearted ♪</i>

42:03.054 --> 42:08.226
<i>♪ Though I try to do more
to fix my soul ♪</i>

42:10.095 --> 42:15.133
<i>♪ I'm trying to be more
than when I started ♪</i>

42:17.636 --> 42:20.572
<i>♪ There's no path before me ♪</i>

42:21.039 --> 42:23.007
<i>♪ gentle music</i>

42:23.008 --> 42:25.110
<i>***</i>

42:55.106 --> 43:05.116
<i>***</i>
